{"type": "article", "id": 12502, "title": "Helix 无线蓝牙耳机", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-23T07:53:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000428efcyGD2TirBzP8lj.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tHelix 是一款无线蓝牙耳机，来自 Ashley Chloe 公司。耳机整体设计简洁明快，配有线控和麦克风，几乎可以兼容所有可以使用蓝牙的智能手机。同时，耳机收起来以后，可以变成一个手环，佩戴在手腕上不容易丢失。颜色上有黑色，白色和红色三款可以选择，目前产品正在 Kickstarter 上面众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1889846331/helix-wearable-cuff-with-stereo-bluetooth-headphon\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140222fbjKIxMVH9WvQ17k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140222wgvhbU86KXiLdIFV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140223bMpuIfWgh6G8qHFC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140224cep1Na3HyAXOMsqf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140224A7BSnHtUkpzwI2oW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140225M5btIFLn2uilrdkQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140226LCcz5wh3SaUrpYkP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60382916\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}